{"tid":267451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨賣香港] 張炳良：一地兩檢法律上可行  商討進度有6成","createTime":"2017-06-02T09:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T00:40:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74401efa62ac55e55ac940f4caf0332eabe8ee0b","tid":267451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496393192_bda0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496393192_bda0.jpg&h=bf940580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段原定明年第三季通車，但爭論多年的「一地兩檢」安排至今仍未落實。房屋及運輸局局長張炳良指，與內地部門有關一地兩檢的商討取得階段性進展，「都六成幾啦」，雙方都認同在基本法下進行一地兩檢，在法律上可行。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良表示一地兩檢當中牽涉到複雜的憲制、法律和操作上的複雜問題，因細節仍在討論進行中，有待與內地進一步確定。記者追問是否能在今個月內公佈，張炳良回應「唔敢咁講，因為討論仲係進行緊。」他指，雖然距離現屆政府任期不足一個月，但會繼續緊守崗位。"},{"pid":"a9426908d5b8ac745349e98615cec06376ddf187","tid":267451,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜？<br />\n一早已經決定咗，而家只係出口術，畀個假希望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e304cb9cef8c9b6bb0f5b3e98eb9427ada4b5974","tid":267451,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}